      "passage_index": 10,
      "title": "Kinfolk (album)",
      "score": 0.0810455490328232,
      "text": "Kinfolk (album)\nKinfolk is the debut and only album by American rap duo Ali & Gipp, released on August 14, 2007, through Derrty Entertainment and Universal Records. The first single off the album was already released, called \"Go 'Head\" featuring Chocolate Tai. The second single is \"N da Paint\" featuring Nelly. The third single is \"Work Dat, Twerk Dat\" featuring Murphy Lee. The fourth and final single is \"Almost Made Ya\" featuring LeToya Luckett.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.05040909109194248,
        "graph": 0.05822331305030371,
        "fact": 0.23902370011442478
      }
