      "title": "Southern Maryland Electric Cooperative",
      "score": 0.1002426485185555,
      "text": "Southern Maryland Electric Cooperative\nThe Southern Maryland Electric Cooperative (SMECO) is an electric distribution cooperative which is headquartered in Hughesville, Maryland. SMECO serves approximately 161,000 customers in Calvert, Charles, Prince George's, and St. Mary's counties of southern Maryland. Under its rules as a nonprofit cooperative, SMECO passes on its costs to its customer-members without markup or profit.",
