      "title": "Hughesville, Maryland",
      "score": 0.09132896463047357,
      "text": "Hughesville, Maryland\nHughesville is a census-designated place (CDP) in Charles County, Maryland, United States. The population was 2,197 at the 2010 census. Truman's Place was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1988.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.05062027391410321,
